---
title: Onion Chutney-Glazed Haloumi & Chicken with Herby Roasted Veggies & Garlic Yoghurt
description: An onion chutney is truly an all-rounder. It can go with anything, so why not try it with squeaky haloumi? It’s going to blow your
mind with the sweet and sticky tastes on top of a roast veggie toss. It’s another win for onion chutney!
